    "description": "As the Lord of the Penguins, you must save the penguin world from monsters. This world is perfect for those who want to experience a third-person shooter roguelite adventure.<br><br>The Lord Penguin can slide and shoot at enemies simultaneously.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/4903b3eec43282d7badce8ee33336bd4.poster.avif?t=1731735461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/4903b3eec43282d7badce8ee33336bd4.webm?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/4903b3eec43282d7badce8ee33336bd4.mp4?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each weapon has its own unique skill attack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/40970913a5a5133030f214193ec721d4.poster.avif?t=1731735461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/40970913a5a5133030f214193ec721d4.webm?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/40970913a5a5133030f214193ec721d4.mp4?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After each wave, you must choose upgrades to prepare for tougher enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/7aa57b7b22eda5fb58bd681ba470133f.poster.avif?t=1731735461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/7aa57b7b22eda5fb58bd681ba470133f.webm?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/7aa57b7b22eda5fb58bd681ba470133f.mp4?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If the monsters hurt you too much, even the Lord Penguin can only survive for so long.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/ee11ff4e31a8ec8f3f9d86bc304b0aea.poster.avif?t=1731735461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/ee11ff4e31a8ec8f3f9d86bc304b0aea.webm?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148880/extras/ee11ff4e31a8ec8f3f9d86bc304b0aea.mp4?t=1731735461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lord of the Penguins offers a fast-paced, fluid, and enjoyable roguelite experience with different play styles. After each run, you can try out different weapons and abilities. With difficulty modes, you can prove to everyone who the real lord is. We invite you, our lord, to save the penguin world!",
